name: Rose Quartz Crystal Rune Stone Set
description: Set consists of 25 crystal runes, a beautifully made black satin-lined velvet bag, and a double sided A4 information sheet, with a few sentences describing each symbol.

name: Designer Desk Notes - Birdsong
description: Designer box with ribbon tab and magnetic closure keeps our charming Bird Song note sheets at your fingertips and complements any desk. Jot down notes, reminders, and spur-of-the-moment ideas on our premium memo sheets with coordinating bird art.

name: Fridrik Karlsson - Magical Christmas
description: This lovely CD features silky smooth nylon guitar, alto flute and also as a special bonus, the famous Bratislava radio orchestra - so we are in for a treat. Traditional Christmas tunes which are recognisable in a high class production where no expense has been spared.

name: Healthy Pregnancy in a Box
description: This recording has been developed to help promote good health for you and your baby during pregnancy and to prepare you both for the birth. It provides the opportunity to work with other members of your family or birthing team and familiarises you with breathing and relaxation techniques which will help during labour and welcome your baby lovingly into the world.

name: Doreen Virtue - Archangel Michael Oracle Cards
description: Archangel Michael is a beloved, powerful protector and trustworthy guide. He knows your life's purpose and the best steps for you to take next.

name: Enchanted Dreams Wall Calendar
description:
Playful, mystical, childlike and wise - spend a year with these enchanting images and may all your dreams come true. 12" x 12" wall calendar by Kristina Swarner. Published by Brush Dance.

 Monthly Quotes:
 Into each life some rain must fall. - Henry Wadsworth Longfellow

 ...my real love has always been the sleep that rescued me by allowing me to dream. - Luigi Pirandello

 Who knows what women can be when they are finally free to become themselves. - Betty Friedan

 Without hope we live in desire. - Dante

name: Chinese Chi Balls
description: Enjoy the perfect Chinese hand-and-foot workout. Now you can unblock and stimulate your chi or life energy, improve your wellbeing - and feel fantastic!

name: Tying the Knot - Complete Wedding Organiser
description:
Use this appealing organizer to turn your wedding dreams into reality! With 108 pages of planning information, craft ideas, and guided note pages, this indispensable volume features organizational necessities: essential information and places to record details about budget, parties, attire, invitations, wedding party, flowers and music, ceremony, reception, and honeymoon. Plastic folders within each of the 9 category sections store and organize papers, receipts, estimates, and samples. The 3-ring binder allows for popping pages in or out. Measures 10-1/2" wide x 11-1/2" high x 1-7/8" deep.
Binding: 3-Ring Binder Use this appealing organizer to turn your wedding dreams into reality! With 108 pages of planning information, craft ideas, and guided note pages, this indispensable volume features organizational necessities.

name: Live With Intention - Renee Locks - Wall Calendar
description:
A year of living intentionally with Renée Locks - sure to nourish, heal and bless the mind, heart and spirit. 12" x 12" wall calendar. Published by Brush Dance.

 Monthly Quotes:
 I don't have to do it the way I did it yesterday. - Unknown

 Cherish your visions, the music that stirs in your heart. - Unknown

 Right now my life is just one learning experience after another. By the end of the week I should be a genius. - Jeanette Osias

 Don't worry if the work is hard and your rewards are few. Remember the mighty oak was once a nut like you! - Unknown

 It's wonderful to get up in the morning knowing you're doing all that you can do. - Unknown

 The important thing is to keep your intention clear. - Straight Arrow

 We grow one petal at a time. - Unknown

 Go easy and if you can't go easy go as easy as you can. - Gertrude Stein

 Taking joy in life is a woman's best cosmetic. - Rosalind Russell

 Breathe, breathe, breathe...

 Too much of a good thing is wonderful. - Mae West

name: Llewellyn - Crystals
description:
Music for Crystal Healing and Relaxation
Crystal Healing is a powerful and effective way to remove blockages and distortions from the human field. It is widely accepted that illness is created in the electromagnetic field around the body and from there it manifests in the physical body only when it is triggered by one factor or another. Crystal Awareness is a wonderful tool of transformation that allows us to tap into our inner resources in addition to stimulating our bodies self healing abilities. This album will encourage you to develop your hidden talents, bringing to the surface forgotten wisdom's enabling you to shine forth as a beacon of light.

name: Llewellyn - Colour Healing
description: The combined vibration of colour and music creates an all encompassing powerhouse of healing energy. The aim has been to produce a healing music album in which each of the individual music tracks vibrate and communicate a key colour on a mental, emotional, physical and spiritual level. For example, RED is a very exciting colour and physically uplifts the spirit with great energy and zest. The music track can be listened to when you need to get yourself going, increase blood circulation and when you feel the need to get on and achieve bigger and better things. Working very closely with Lilian Verner Bonds, the well known Author and vice-president of the International Association of Colour Therapists, Colour Healing is a unique album that captures the vibration of colours and enables us to use it in our daily lives to consciously influence our Mind, Body and Soul to promote happiness, health and harmony.

name: Philip Guyler - Essential Reiki
description: Reiki is a Japanese word meaning Universal Life Energy and is a deep, powerful, healing and cleansing technique for the whole of the mind, body and spirit. Essential Reiki is an album that has been ideally timed for treatments by Reiki practitioners and will allow them to concentrate on Reiki and ignore the clock. The music is also versatile enough to be used for self treatment, meditation, attunement, relaxation and creation of a calm, peaceful and tranquil ambience for individuals as well. Twelve five minute tracks especially composed to create a deep, powerful embrace and enjoy the benefits of the techniques being practiced either personally or by a Reiki practitioner.

name: Designer Desk Notes - Dragonfly
description: Designer box with ribbon tab and magnetic closure keeps our charming Bird Song note sheets at your fingertips and complements any desk. Jot down notes, reminders, and spur-of-the-moment ideas on our premium memo sheets with coordinating bird art.

name: Blank Note Cards - Peace Out
description: Write on! These groovy note cards are perfect for your personal correspondence. (Boxed stationery cards make great gifts, too!)

name: Shamindra, Gayle Berry - Baby Massage
description: Baby Massage is a wonderful and special gift that you can share with your baby. This form of massage has been practised for hundreds of years in many diverse cultures to meet a variety of baby's physical and emotional needs. Babies crave skin contact. The first sense that develops in the womb is touch and through the medium of massage you can communicate love and security to your baby as soon as he is born. Everyone has the ability to touch and soothe their infant. Massage is simply a method to re-inforce this natural ability and to help reassure and calm your baby. Baby Massage has numerous physical and emotional benefits for your baby and can help you learn more about your baby and his behaviour. It also provides the perfect opportunity to relax, have fun and bond with your baby. Includes a full colour guide.

name: Blank Note Cards - Dragonfly
description: Let your words take wing with these exuberant Dragonfly Note Cards! Boxed personal stationery note cards feature a soft, appealing Eastern-inspired design motif embossed with glossy highlights.

name: Louise L. Hay - Power Thought Cards
description: A deck of 64 affirmation cards to help you find your inner strength. 'Affirmations are like planting seeds in the ground, it takes some time to go from a seed to a full-grown plant.'

name: Tao Wall Calendar
description:
The Tao Te Ching, the esoteric but infinitely practical book written in the sixth century BC by Lao Tsu, has been translated more times than any work except the Bible. For centuries, artists, poets, painters and even gardeners have used the Tao Te Ching as a source of inspiration and guidance. The Tao wall calendar features contemplative nature photographs, gracefully stylized Chinese calligraphy and translations of the Tao Te Ching and Chuang Tsu: Inner Chapters.

 Photography by Jane English. Calligraphy by Gai-Fu Feng

name: Pregnancy Journal
description: With ample pages to record your discoveries and feelings, and a pregnancy guide offering concise, time-targeted information, this companion journal helps light the path and preserve the wonder as you move toward motherhood!

name: Mini Wall Calendar - Jewel of the Lotus
description:
The auspicious lotus symbolises beauty, purity and enlightenment. Enjoy a full year of images and inspirational words.

 Sample text; We must have richness of the soul.

name: Meditation Wall Calendar
description:
Featuring a collection of meditative images paired with thoughtful quotes from a variety of spiritual traditions, inspiring both clarity and serenity. A gentle tool to support and encourage your practice, this calendar will help cleanse your mind and body of stress and will guide you on a path toward reflection, health and spiritual awakening. 12" x 12" Wall Calendar. Published by Amber Lotus.

 Sample text; Nothing in all creation is so like God as stillness. Meister Eckhart

name: Louise L. Hay - You Can Heal Your Life - Wall Calendar
description:
In her powerful, pioneering and inspirational book You Can Heal Your Life, Louise L. Hay, widely regarded as one of the founders of the self-help movement, explains how our beliefs and ideas can be the cause of illness and how changing our thinking can improve our quality of life.

 Every month of the 12" x 12" wall calendar features an insightful quote, teaching text and a helpful affirmation, all illustrated with the charming artwork of Joan Perrin-Falquet. Published by Amber Lotus.

name: Laugh Lines - Renee Locks - Wall Calendar
description:
The whimsical art and insights of Renée Locks' Laugh Lines invites us to live a little and laugh a lot each and every day. 12" x 12" wall calendar. Published by Brush Dance.

 Monthly Quotes:
 Inside me lives a skinny woman crying to get out, but I usually shut her up with a cookie. - Unknown

 Blessed is she who can laugh at herself for she shall never cease to be amused. - Unknown

 Housework can't kill you. But why take a chance. - Phyllis Diller

 Every path has its puddle. - Proverb

 I have been called bitch so often sounds like I love you to me.

 It is better to be looked over than to be overlooked. - Mae West

 If you're run out of town, get in front of the crowd, and make it look like a parade. - Sally Stanford

 Cooperation is doing with a smile what you have to do anyway. - Unknown

 Almost everything I know today I learned by listening to myself when I didn't know what I was talking about. - Gracie Allen

 Your dresses should be tight enough to show you're a woman and loose enough to show you're a lady. - Edith Head

 Be it ever so humble there's no place like home for wearing what you like. - George Ade

 If you're going to walk on thin ice - you might as well dance. - Unknown

name: Dr Wayne Dyer - Living the Wisdom of the Tao
description: More than two millennia ago, the great Chinese sage Lao-tzu dictated the Tao Te Ching, or the Great Way, now regarded by many to be the ultimate commentary on the nature of our existence. This profound spiritual text offers practical guidance for living in a new world aligned with nature. The Living the Wisdom of the Tao wall calendar, based on Dr. Wayne Dyer’s best-selling book Change Your Thoughts -- Change Your Life, pairs ethereal Taoist photography with quotes from the Tao Te Ching and Dyer's commentary on how to apply this ancient wisdom in our modern world.

name: Butterfly Wings Wall Calendar
description:
Butterfly Wings 2014 Wall Calendar

 Floating and free, let these elegant winged creatures created by Cynthia Louden find their way into your heart and imagination. 12" x 12" wall calendar. Published by Brush Dance.

 Monthly Quotes:
 Let yourself be silently drawn by the stronger pull of what you really love. - Rumi

 Love does not consist in gazing at each other but in looking together in the same direction. - Antoine de Saint-Exupry

 Every great dream begins with a dreamer. -Harriet Tubman

 Even after all this time, The sun never says to the earth, "You owe me." Look what happens with a love like that. It lights the whole sky. - Hafiz

 Wake at dawn with a winged heart and give thanks for another day of loving. - Kahlil Gibran

 Every day is a journey, and the journey itself is home.- Basho

 Progress lies not in enhancing what is, but in advancing toward what will be. - Kahlil Gibran

 First say to yourself what you would be; and then do what you have to do. - Epictetus

 Life is either a daring adventure or nothing. To keep our faces toward change and behave like free spirits in the presence of fate is strength undefeatable. - Helen Keller

name: Louise L. Hay - You Can Heal Your Life (DVD)
description: This film gives penetrating insights into Louise's fascinating personal story and shows how her views on self-esteem, abundance, and the metaphysical causes behind physical ailments were developed.

name: Barbel Mohr - Cosmic Ordering: Why It Works
description: Cosmic Ordering is the powerful method of tuning into the universe to turn dreams into reality. Barbel Mohr is the woman credited with creating this amazing system.

name: Amethyst (Namibia)
description: Indications: Sobriety, purity, composure, calm, helps with tiredness, anxiety, habitual tendencies and addictions, good for lungs, large intestine, skin, alleviates itching and sunburn

name: Mini Meditations for Stress Free Living
description: Think you haven't got the time to meditate? Think again! These "mini" meditations are perfectly suited to relieve the stress resulting from our busy lifestyles.

name: Mindfulness Meditation for Pain Relief
description: Also included is a four page booklet explaining Vidamala's unique techniques and how to get the maximum benefit from the practices.

name: Meditations to Connect With Archangel Gabriel
description:
9 tracks, 50 minutes approx. This magnificent journey will help you to: 
connect with Archangel Gabriel 
dissolve all your worries 
rekindle hope 
find the clarity to manifest a wonderful future 
listen to Archangel Gabriel's wisdom

name: Meditation to Connect With Archangel Michael
description:
15 tracks, 44 minutes approx. In this powerful meditation you will: connect with Archangel Michael
find your power and inner strength 
release your burdens 
be freed from emotional ties 
enhance your leadership qualities

name: Louise L. Hay - Receiving Prosperity
description: Are you as wealthy and successful as you'd like to be? Whether you realise it or not, your level of wealth and success reflects exactly what you believe you deserve.

name: Enchanted Meditations for Kids
description: This CD can be used at home with your children or as a teaching resource. The meditations are preceded by a relaxation exercise which can be used separately or they can run together as one track.

name: Dr Wayne Dyer - Meditations for Manifesting
description: Morning and evening meditations to literally create your heart's desire. Make no mistake about it - you can manifest ANYTHING you want in life when you connect with the abundance in the Universe.

name: Doreen Virtue - Angel Medicine
description: While researching her book Angel Medicine, Doreen Virtue began taking her workshop participants through a meditation so that they could experience a vicarious trip to an Atlantean healing temple.

name: Brandon Bays - The Journey (CD)
description: This CD accompanies The Journey (book). "Brandon's inspiring story is proof of the healing power that exists within every individual' - John Gray, author of Men Are from Mars, Women Are from Venus

name: The Ultimate Pregnancy Organiser
description: Conveniently structured by trimesters, this comprehensive planner covers everything from conception to the birth and beyond.

name: Rosemary Ellen Guiley - An Angel in Your Pocket
description: They don't wear wings, they don't live on clouds, but they do come into our lives...

name: Michael Gienger - Healing Crystals
description: All the important information about 430 healing gem-stones in a neat pocket-book!

name: Meditations with James van Praagh
description: James Van Praagh is justly famous as one of the most successful spiritual mediums of our time. His first book, Talking to Heaven, was a Number One bestseller and his demonstrations draw huge crowds around the world.

name: Louise L. Hay - You Can Heal Your Life
description: The definitive bestselling book on self-healing has transformed the lives of millions of people. This is a book that people credit with profoundly altering their awareness of the impact that the mind has on our health and well-being.

name: Lisa Montanaro - The Ultimate Life Organiser
description: Here is your very own portable personal organizer and life coach, offering easy-to-follow steps on the way to an organized, empowered life! Author Lisa Montanaro is a Certified Professional Organizer, life coach, and motivational speaker.

name: Judy Hall - The Crystal Experience (with CD)
description: The Crystal Experience is a complete crystal workshop in one book. Interactive and practical, the step-by-step learning programme will guide you towards the profound wisdom within crystal lore.

name: Jude Reignier - Easy Yoga
description: Small book. Jude Reignier's 'Easy Yoga' is based on her ten years' teaching experience and will appeal to adults and children alike, plus those with special needs

name: John Gray - Men are From Mars, Women are From Venus
description: This is a world-known book. From casual daters searching for a soulmate to married couples who think they've got nothing to learn, John Gray's straightforward, honest insight and advice has transformed the relationships of millions.

name: Florence Scovel-Shinn - The Game of Life and How to Play It
description: "This absolute gem of a book lays down the rules of how to play the game of life and win, by providing the key principles to happiness and fulfilment." - Watkins Books, London

name: Doreen Virtue and Judith Lukomski - Crystal Therapy
description: How to heal and empower your life with crystal energy. Crystal Therapy is a handy guide to the healing power of 94 crystals, complete with beautiful colour photographs of each crystal family.

name: Doreen Virtue - The Miracles of Archangel Michael
description: Archangel Michael has long been a protector of, and friends to, all who ask. Healer, warrior and guardian, Michael is the bringer of peace and the conqueror of darkness.

name: Doreen Virtue - How to Hear Your Angels
description: This is a step-by-step guide to clearly receiving messages from your angels and guides. This material has been collected from Doreen Virtue's bestseller 'Messages from Your Angels' and from her workshops.

name: Brenda Mallon - The Dream Bible
description: The definitive guide to over 300 dream symbols. The Dream Bible is a comprehensive guide to the universal symbols and themes that appear in our dreams. Beautifully illustrated throughout.

name: Doreen Virtue - Romance Angels
description: The Romance Angels are a group of cherubic angels who are focused upon all things love related. Anyone can call upon these beings, and they're able to help unlimited numbers of people simultaneously. Guidebook included.

name: Doreen Virtue - Messages From Your Angels
description: This card deck makes it easier than ever to give an amazingly accurate angel reading for yourself or others. Each card features a gorgeous angel paining, along with a one- or two-sentence message. Guidebook included

name: Doreen Virtue - Daily Guidance From Your Angels
description: These oracle cards (with accompanying guidebook) provide messages and reminders of your guardian angels' steady and loving presence.

name: Diana Cooper - Teen Angel Cards
description: Love yourself. Do your best. Don't judge others. Quit worrying. Do your schoolwork. Listen to others. Just a few of the sayings on these lovely teen cards.

name: Barbel Mohr - Cosmic Ordering Oracle Cards
description: From the author who brought us the bestselling 'Cosmic Ordering for Beginners' comes a new way to communicate with the cosmos. Listen to your inner voice, pick a card, and take meaning from what the cosmos delivers.
